    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225730/extras/e5361f5e78df2fef52b21e9c92213c8a.poster.avif?t=1772433355\" width=1170 height=798 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225730/extras/e5361f5e78df2fef52b21e9c92213c8a.webm?t=1772433355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225730/extras/6f02b5c108d5116eea3bb519a856faae.avif?t=1772433355\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>你的塔罗牌在这里字面意义上决定了你的命运。拥有超过100张卡牌和无数组合来构筑你的套牌，</strong><br><strong>每一次抽牌，都是全新的命运。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225730/extras/5ae14b4991ae4834ecef0d80087cab93.poster.avif?t=1772433355\" width=1138 height=536 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225730/extras/5ae14b4991ae4834ecef0d80087cab93.webm?t=1772433355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225730/extras/6a5246f3d0586eb82da3cd14c971e6e2.avif?t=1772433355\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>通过数百个独特的对话与事件，揭开属于你自己的故事，在探索中逐渐理解生命的奥秘、死亡之后的真相，</strong><br><strong>以及主宰两者的神秘存在。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225730/extras/586c8cb7fb1cad6dd399d86d75824ee7.poster.avif?t=1772433355\" width=1138 height=776 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225730/extras/586c8cb7fb1cad6dd399d86d75824ee7.webm?t=1772433355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225730/extras/586c8cb7fb1cad6dd399d86d75824ee7.mp4?t=1772433355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225730/extras/d7df2cb143f91a629bae9a53c72be660.avif?t=1772433355\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>拥有50多个神秘事件、60多种战斗组合、100多件遗物和20多种消耗品，彼岸世界保证——没有两段旅程会是相同的。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225730/extras/556236dc164418606973316b36d02e63.poster.avif?t=1772433355\" width=1170 height=551 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225730/extras/556236dc164418606973316b36d02e63.webm?t=1772433355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225730/extras/75b72a35b8cb45b5513525b0b4744f7a.avif?t=1772433355\" width=1232 height=580 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>想知道这一切的意义吗？想知道你是怎么来到这里的？你的名字？我本可以告诉你……不过，世上可没有免费的交易。但如果你给我一个机会，我保证你大概不会后悔。——本店营业中！ 以下是一些满意顾客的评价：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225730/extras/0df65e49533afecf5d53430a1b4f5fcf.avif?t=1772433355\" width=1232 height=1840 /></span></p>",
